</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[199,1196,297,323]" pageId="52" pageNumber="53" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="52.[151,1437,152,323]" box="[199,1196,297,323]" pageId="52" pageNumber="53">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,297,323]" pageId="52" pageNumber="53">Etymology.</emphasis>
The species is named after its 
<typeStatus box="[678,726,297,323]" pageId="52" pageNumber="53">type</typeStatus>
locality—Arava desert in southern 
<collectingCountry box="[1126,1192,297,323]" name="Israel" pageId="52" pageNumber="53">Israel</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
